    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Territories belonging to or recently having belonged to one political entity, but through military occupation or other provisional control are held by another political entity without the volition of original entity.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
